# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LocalDiabetic Home Vault — PHI GUARD
# This repo is a TEMPLATE. Real personal health records must NEVER
# be committed. Enforces HARD-INVARIANT.md at the git layer:
# raw PHI never leaves the local box.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Scanned / photographed documents (records, cards, letters)
*.pdf
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.heic
*.tif
*.tiff
*.bmp
*.gif
*.webp

# Office / exported records
*.doc
*.docx
*.xls
*.xlsx
*.csv
*.numbers
*.pages

# Anything a user marks as their own filled-in copy
*-MINE.md
*-FILLED.md
*.private.md
/**/my-*.md

# Generated notes & receipts hold real activity — keep them local
13-organized-notes/*
!13-organized-notes/README.md
14-receipts/*
!14-receipts/README.md

# Reminder engine — the user's real schedule + activity stay on the box
engine/reminders.json
engine/.state/
!engine/reminders.example.json

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/
